```

The class is already exported from `src/models.js` (line 8736). It is **not** currently
imported in `pipelines.js`.

---

### Step 2 — Add JSDoc typedefs in `src/pipelines.js`

Insert immediately **before** the `ImageClassificationSingle` typedef block (the line
`* @typedef {Object} ImageClassificationSingle` which follows the closing `}` of
`ImageToTextPipeline`):

